02 Set top-level identity: `version: \"0.0.2\"`, `type: \"plugin\"`, `author: \"volcano-sh\"`, `name: \"agentcube\"`\n37: - [ ] T-003.03 Set `label` map with `en_US`, `ja_JP`, `zh_Hans`, `pt_BR` all → `\"Agentcube\"`\n38: - [ ] T-003.04 Set `description` as multilingual map with localized AgentCube descriptions\n39: - [ ] T-003.05 Set `icon: \"icon.png\"` and `icon_dark: \"icon-dark.png\"`\n40: - [ ] T-003.06 Set `resource` with `memory` and `permission` subtree (flags and sizes for `tool`, `model`, `endpoint`, `app`, `storage`)\n41: - [ ] T-003.07 Set `plugins.tools: [provider/agentcube.yaml]`\n42: - [ ] T-003.08 Set `meta` with `version`, `arch: [amd64, arm64]`, `runner` (`language: \"python\"`, `version: \"3.12\"`, `entrypoint: \"main\"`), `minimum_dify_version: null`\n43: - [ ] T-003.09 Set `created_at`, `privacy`, `repo`, `verified` fields\n44: \n45: **验收**: `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml')); assert d['version']=='0.0.2'; assert d['type']=='plugin'; assert d['author']=='volcano-sh'; assert d['name']=='agentcube'; assert d['meta']['runner']['language']=='python'; assert d['plugins.tools']==['provider/agentcube.yaml']\"` 退出码 0\n46: \n47: ---\n48: \n49: ### T-004: Create `requirements.txt` for plugin dependencies\n50: \n51: - [ ] T-004.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt`\n52: - [ ] T-004.02 Pin `dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0`\n53: - [ ] T-004.03 Pin `agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10`\n54: \n55: **验收**: `grep 'dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0' integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt` 有输出; `grep 'agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10' integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt` 有输出\n56: \n57: ---\n58: \n59: ## Phase 2: Provider Descriptor & Implementation\n60: \n61: ### T-005: Create `provider/agentcube.yaml` tool provider descriptor\n62: \n63: - [ ] T-005.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml`\n64: - [ ] T-005.02 Define `identity` with `author`, `name`, multilingual `label`, multilingual `description`, and `icon`\n65: - [ ] T-005.03 Include commented-out `oauth_schema` block (present as YAML comments only)\n66: - [ ] T-005.04 Set `tools: [tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml]`\n67: - [ ] T-005.05 Set `extra.python.source: \"provider/agentcube.py\"`\n68: \n69: **验收**: `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml')); assert 'identity' in d; assert d['tools']==['tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml']; assert d['extra']['python']['source']=='provider/agentcube.py'\"` 退出码 0; `grep '#.*oauth_schema' integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml` 有输出（注释形式存在）\n70: \n71: ---\n72: \n73: ### T-006: Create `provider/agentcube.py` provider implementation\n74: \n75: - [ ] T-006.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py`\n76: - [ ] T-006.02 Import `ToolProvider` from `dify_plugin`\n77: - [ ] T-006.03 Import `ToolProviderCredentialValidationError` from `dify_plugin.errors.tool`\n78: - [ ] T-006.04 Define `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider(ToolProvider)` class\n79: - [ ] T-006.05 Implement `_validate_credentials(self, credentials: dict[str, Any]) -> None` with try/except that raises `ToolProviderCredentialValidationError(str(e))` on failure\n80: - [ ] T-006.06 Successful validation returns `None` without raising\n81: \n82: **验收**: `python3 -c \"\n83: import ast, sys\n84: tree = ast.parse(open('integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py').read())\n85: classes = [n for n in ast.walk(tree) if isinstance(n, ast.ClassDef)]\n86: assert any(n.name == 'AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider' for n in classes), 'Class not found'\n87: methods = [n for c in classes if c.name == 'AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider' for n in ast.walk(c) if isinstance(n, ast.FunctionDef) and n.name == '_validate_credentials']\n88: assert len(methods) == 1, '_validate_credentials not found'\n89: \" ` 退出码 0; `grep 'ToolProviderCredentialValidationError' integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py` 有输出\n90: \n91: ---\n92: \n93: ## Phase 3: Tool Schema & Implementation\n94: \n95: ### T-007: Create `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml` tool schema\n96: \n97: - [ ] T-007.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml`\n98: - [ ] T-007.02 Define `identity` with `name: \"agentcube-code-interpreter\"`, `author: \"agentcube\"`, multilingual `label`/`description` (human + llm)\n99: - [ ] T-007.03 Define required parameter `router_url` (type: string, required: true, form: form)\n100: - [ ] T-007.04 Define required parameter `workload_manager_url` (type: string, required: true, form: form)\n101: - [ ] T-007.05 Define optional parameter `language` (type: select, required: false, form: llm, options: `[python, javascript, typescript]`)\n102: - [ ] T-007.06 Define optional parameters: `code` (string), `command` (string), `session_id` (string), `session_reuse` (boolean), `code_interpreter_id` (string), all with `required: false`, `form: llm`\n103: - [ ] T-007.07 Each parameter includes `name`, `type`, `required`, `label`, `human_description`, `llm_description`, `form`\n104: - [ ] T-007.08 Set `extra.python.source: \"tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py\"`\n105: \n106: **验收**: `python3 -c \"\n107: import yaml\n108: d = yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml'))\n109: assert d['identity']['name'] == 'agentcube-code-interpreter'\n110: params = {p['name']: p for p in d['parameters']}\n111: assert params['router_url']['required'] == True\n112: assert params['workload_manager_url']['required'] == True\n113: assert params['language']['type'] == 'select'\n114: assert set(params['language']['options']) == {'python', 'javascript', 'typescript'}\n115: assert params['session_reuse']['type'] == 'boolean'\n116: assert d['extra']['python']['source'] == 'tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py'\n117: \"` 退出码 0\n118: \n119: ---\n120: \n121: ### T-008: Create `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py` tool implementation\n122: \n123: - [ ] T-008.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py`\n124: - [ ] T-008.02 Import `Tool` from `dify_plugin`, `ToolInvokeMessage` from `dify_plugin.entities.tool`, `CodeInterpreterClient` from `agentcube`\n125: - [ ] T-008.03 Import `Generator` from `collections.abc` and `Any` from `typing`\n126: - [ ] T-008.04 Define `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool(Tool)` class\n127: - [ ] T-008.05 Implement `_invoke(self, tool_parameters: dict[str, Any]) -> Generator[ToolInvokeMessage]` that calls `self.execute(**tool_parameters)` and yields `self.create_json_message(result)`\n128: - [ ] T-008.06 Implement `execute` with parameters: `router_url`, `workload_manager_url`, `language=\"python\"`, `code_interpreter_id`, `session_id`, `code`, `command`, `session_reuse=False`, `**kwargs`\n129: - [ ] T-008.07 `execute` delegates to `CodeInterpreterClient` from `agentcube` for remote operations\n130: - [ ] T-008.08 `execute` returns JSON-serializable result\n131: \n132: **验收**: `python3 -c \"\n133: import ast\n134: tree = ast.parse(open('integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py').read())\n135: classes = [n for n in ast.walk(tree) if isinstance(n, ast.ClassDef)]\n136: assert any(n.name == 'AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool' for n in classes)\n137: methods = [n.name for c in classes if c.name == 'AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool' for n in ast.walk(c) if isinstance(n, ast.FunctionDef)]\n138: assert '_invoke' in methods\n139: assert 'execute' in methods\n140: \"` 退出码 0; `grep 'from agentcube import CodeInterpreterClient' integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py` 有输出; `grep 'create_json_message' integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py` 有输出\n141: \n142: ---\n143: \n144: ## Phase 4: Plugin Documentation & Packaging\n145: \n146: ### T-009: Create plugin documentation files\n147: \n148: - [ ] T-009.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/GUIDE.md` with plugin usage guide\n149: - [ ] T-009.02 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/README.md` with plugin documentation\n150: - [ ] T-009.03 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/PRIVACY.md` with privacy policy\n151: - [ ] T-009.04 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/.difyignore` with ignore patterns\n152: \n153: **验收**: `ls integrations/dify-plugin/GUIDE.md integrations/dify-plugin/README.md integrations/dify-plugin/PRIVACY.md integrations/dify-plugin/.difyignore` 四个文件均存在\n154: \n155: ---\n156: \n157: ## Phase 5: PCAP Analyzer FastAPI Service\n158: \n159: ### T-010: Create `example/pcap-analyzer/` directory and `requirements.txt`\n160: \n161: - [ ] T-010.01 Create `example/pcap-analyzer/` directory\n162: - [ ] T-010.02 Create `example/pcap-analyzer/requirements.txt`\n163: - [ ] T-010.03 Pin `fastapi==0.120.0` and `uvicorn==0.38.0`\n164: - [ ] T-010.04 Pin LangChain stack: `langchain==1.0.2`, `langchain-classic==1.0.0`, `langchain-community==0.4.1`, `langchain-core==1.0.1`, `langchain-openai==1.0.1`, `langchain-text-splitters==1.0.0`\n165: - [ ] T-010.05 Pin LangGraph stack: `langgraph==1.0.1`, `langgraph-checkpoint==3.0.0`, `langgraph-prebuilt==1.0.1`, `langgraph-sdk==0.2.9`, `langsmith==0.4.38`\n166: - [ ] T-010.06 Pin `paramiko==4.0.0` and `python-multipart==0.0.20`\n167: - [ ] T-010.07 Ensure `agentcube` is NOT listed (vendored via Dockerfile)\n168: \n169: **验收**: `grep 'fastapi==0.120.0' example/pcap-analyzer/requirements.txt` 有输出; `grep 'langgraph==1.0.1' example/pcap-analyzer/requirements.txt` 有输出; `grep 'paramiko==4.0.0' example/pcap-analyzer/requirements.txt` 有输出; `grep 'agentcube' example/pcap-analyzer/requirements.txt` 无输出\n170: \n171: ---\n172: \n173: ### T-011: Create `pcap_analyzer.py` — Config, agents, and SandboxRunner\n174: \n175: - [ ] T-011.01 Create `example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py`\n176: - [ ] T-011.02 Define config constants: `API_KEY` from `OPENAI_API_KEY` (required), `API_BASE_URL` from `OPENAI_API_BASE` (default `https://api.siliconflow.cn/v1`), `MODEL_NAME` from `OPENAI_MODEL` (default `Qwen/QwQ-32B`), `CODEINTERPRETER_NAME` (default `my-interpreter`), `SANDBOX_NAMESPACE` (default `default`), `SANDBOX_WARMUP_SEC` (default `5`), `SERVER_HOST=\"0.0.0.0\"`, `SERVER_PORT=8000`, `SERVER_RELOAD=True`\n177: - [ ] T-011.03 Implement `SandboxRunner` class with `__init__(name=\"my-interpreter\", namespace=\"default\", warmup_sec=5)`, `upload_file(local_path, remote_path) -> bool`, `upload_bytes(data, remote_path) -> bool`, `run(command) -> Dict[str, Any]`, `stop()`\n178: - [ ] T-011.04 Implement `build_react_agent(llm, system_prompt)` using `langgraph.prebuilt.create_react_agent`\n179: - [ ] T-011.05 Implement `invoke_react_agent(agent, user_text) -> str`\n180: - [ ] T-011.06 Implement `build_planner_agent(llm)` for script planning\n181: - [ ] T-011.07 Implement `build_reporter_agent(llm)` for report generation\n182: \n183: **验收**: `python3 -c \"\n184: import ast\n185: tree = ast.parse(open('example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py').read())\n186: classes = [n.name for n in ast.walk(tree) if isinstance(n, ast.ClassDef)]\n187: funcs = [n.name for n in ast.walk(tree) if isinstance(n, ast.FunctionDef) or isinstance(n, ast.AsyncFunctionDef)]\n188: assert 'SandboxRunner' in classes\n189: assert 'build_react_agent' in funcs\n190: assert 'build_planner_agent' in funcs\n191: assert 'build_reporter_agent' in funcs\n192: assert 'invoke_react_agent' in funcs\n193: \"` 退出码 0; `grep 'api.siliconflow.cn/v1' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出; `grep 'Qwen/QwQ-32B' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出\n194: \n195: ---\n196: \n197: ### T-012: Create `pcap_analyzer.py` — Orchestration functions\n198: \n199: - [ ] T-012.01 Implement `_plan_script(agent, pcap_local_path) -> str` for plan script generation\n200: - [ ] T-012.02 Implement `_repair_script(agent, prev_script, results) -> str` for script repair\n201: - [ ] T-012.03 Implement `_execute_once_in_runner(runner, pcap_local_path, script) -> List[Dict[str, Any]]` that uploads PCAP, executes script, returns result list\n202: - [ ] T-012.04 Implement `_analyze_with_retries(planner, reporter, runner, pcap_local_path, max_retries=2) -> Dict[str, Any]` with planning, execution, repair loop\n203: - [ ] T-012.05 Implement `_report(agent, results) -> str` for report generation\n204: \n205: **验收**: `grep '_plan_script' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出; `grep '_repair_script' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出; `grep '_execute_once_in_runner' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出; `grep '_analyze_with_retries' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出; `grep '_report' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出\n206: \n207: ---\n208: \n209: ### T-013: Create `pcap_analyzer.py` — FastAPI app and `/analyze` endpoint\n210: \n211: - [ ] T-013.01 Define `AnalyzeResponse(BaseModel)` with `script: str`, `results: List[Dict[str, Any]]`, `report: str`\n212: - [ ] T-013.02 Create `FastAPI(title=\"PCAP Analyzer — Env-Only Config\")` app instance\n213: - [ ] T-013.03 Implement `@app.on_event(\"startup\")` async `on_startup()` that validates `OPENAI_API_KEY`, builds `ChatOpenAI`, `PLANNER`, `REPORTER` agents; fails startup if API key missing\n214: - [ ] T-013.04 Implement `async def analyze_endpoint(pcap_file: UploadFile = File(None), pcap_path: str = Form(None))` with `response_model=AnalyzeResponse`\n215: - [ ] T-013.05 Endpoint returns 400 if neither `pcap_file` nor `pcap_path` provided\n216: - [ ] T-013.06 Endpoint handles file upload and file path cases, calls `_analyze_with_retries`, returns `AnalyzeResponse`\n217: - [ ] T-013.07 Add `if __name__ == \"__main__\": uvicorn.run(...)` entry with `SERVER_HOST`, `SERVER_PORT`, `SERVER_RELOAD`\n218: \n219: **验收**: `python3 -c \"\n220: import ast\n221: tree = ast.parse(open('example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py').read())\n222: classes = [n.name for n in ast.walk(tree) if isinstance(n, ast.ClassDef)]\n223: assert 'AnalyzeResponse' in classes\n224: funcs = [n.name for n in ast.walk(tree) if isinstance(n, ast.AsyncFunctionDef)]\n225: assert 'analyze_endpoint' in funcs\n226: assert 'on_startup' in funcs\n227: \"` 退出码 0; `grep 'response_model=AnalyzeResponse' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出; `grep 'UploadFile' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出; `grep 'OPENAI_API_KEY' example/pcap-analyzer/pcap_analyzer.py` 有输出\n228: \n229: ---\n230: \n231: ## Phase 6: PCAP Analyzer Container & Kubernetes\n232: \n233: ### T-014: Create `example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile`\n234: \n235: - [ ] T-014.01 Create `example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile`\n236: - [ ] T-014.02 Use base image `ghcr.io/astral-sh/uv:python3.12-bookworm-slim`\n237: - [ ] T-014.03 Run `uv venv` and `uv pip install -r requirements.txt`\n238: - [ ] T-014.04 Copy `sdk-python/agentcube` to `./agentcube/` (vendored SDK)\n239: - [ ] T-014.05 Copy `pcap_analyzer.py` to `./`\n240: - [ ] T-014.06 Set `ENV PYTHONPATH=\"/app\"`\n241: - [ ] T-014.07 `EXPOSE 8000`\n242: - [ ] T-014.08 `CMD [\"uv\", \"run\", \"pcap_analyzer.py\"]`\n243: \n244: **验收**: `grep 'ghcr.io/astral-sh/uv:python3.12-bookworm-slim' example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` 有输出; `grep 'uv pip install' example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` 有输出; `grep 'sdk-python/agentcube' example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` 有输出; `grep 'PYTHONPATH' example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` 有输出; `grep 'EXPOSE 8000' example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` 有输出; `grep 'uv.*run.*pcap_analyzer.py' example/pcap-analyzer/Dockerfile` 有输出\n245: \n246: ---\n247: \n248: ### T-015: Create `example/pcap-analyzer/deployment.yaml` Kubernetes manifest\n249: \n250: - [ ] T-015.01 Create `example/pcap-analyzer/deployment.yaml`\n251: - [ ] T-015.02 Define `Deployment` with `metadata.name: \"pcap-analyzer\"`, `metadata.namespace: \"default\"`\n252: - [ ] T-015.03 Container `pcap-analyzer`, image `pcap-analyzer:latest`, `imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent`\n253: - [ ] T-015.04 Container port `8000` TCP\n254: - [ ] T-015.05 Resource requests: `cpu: \"200m\"`, `memory: \"100Mi\"`\n255: - [ ] T-015.06 Resource limits: `cpu: \"1\"`, `memory: \"1Gi\"`\n256: - [ ] T-015.07 Env `OPENAI_API_KEY` from Secret `pcap-analyzer-secrets` key `openai-api-key`\n257: - [ ] T-015.08 Plain env vars: `OPENAI_API_BASE`, `OPENAI_MODEL`, `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`, `ROUTER_URL`, `CODEINTERPRETER_NAME`, `SANDBOX_NAMESPACE`, `SANDBOX_WARMUP_SEC`\n258: - [ ] T-015.09 Command: `[\"uv\"]`, args: `[\"run\", \"pcap_analyzer.py\"]`\n259: \n260: **验收**: `python3 -c \"\n261: import yaml\n262: d = yaml.safe_load(open('example/pcap-analyzer/deployment.yaml'))\n263: assert d['kind'] == 'Deployment'\n264: assert d['metadata']['name'] == 'pcap-analyzer'\n265: container = d['spec']['template']['spec']['containers'][0]\n266: assert container['image'] == 'pcap-analyzer:latest'\n267: assert container['ports'][0]['containerPort'] == 8000\n268: assert container['resources']['requests']['cpu'] == '200m'\n269: assert container['resources']['limits']['memory'] == '1Gi'\n270: env_names = [e['name'] for e in container['env']]\n271: assert 'OPENAI_API_KEY' in env_names\n272: assert 'OPENAI_API_BASE' in env_names\n273: assert container['command'] == ['uv']\n274: assert container['args'] == ['run', 'pcap_analyzer.py']\n275: \"` 退出码 0\n276: \n277: ---\n278: \n279: ### T-016: Create `example/pcap-analyzer/README.md`\n280: \n281: - [ ] T-016.01 Create `example/pcap-analyzer/README.md` with usage documentation, environment variables, Docker build instructions, and Kubernetes deployment guide\n282: \n283: **验收**: `test -s example/pcap-analyzer/README.md` 文件存在且非空\n284: \n285: ---\n286: \n287: ## Phase 7: Tests\n288: \n289: ### T-017: Create Dify plugin tests\n290: \n291: - [ ] T-017.01 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/tests/` directory\n292: - [ ] T-017.02 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/tests/test_provider.py` — test `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider._validate_credentials` raises on error, passes on success\n293: - [ ] T-017.03 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/tests/test_tool.py` — test `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool._invoke` yields JSON message, `execute` delegates to SDK\n294: - [ ] T-017.04 Create `integrations/dify-plugin/tests/test_manifest.py` — test manifest.yaml structure, provider descriptor, tool schema parse correctly\n295: \n296: **验收**: `ls integrations/dify-plugin/tests/test_provider.py integrations/dify-plugin/tests/test_tool.py integrations/dify-plugin/tests/test_manifest.py` 三个文件均存在\n297: \n298: ---\n299: \n300: ### T-018: Create PCAP analyzer tests\n301: \n302: - [ ] T-018.01 Create `example/pcap-analyzer/tests/` directory\n303: - [ ] T-018.02 Create `example/pcap-analyzer/tests/test_pcap_analyzer.py` — test `/analyze` endpoint with TestClient, mock agents, valid `AnalyzeResponse`; test startup fails without API key\n304: - [ ] T-018.03 Create `example/pcap-analyzer/tests/test_sandbox_runner.py` — test `upload_file`, `upload_bytes`, `run`, `stop` with mocked `CodeInterpreterClient`\n305: - [ ] T-018.04 Create `example/pcap-analyzer/tests/test_agents.py` — test `build_react_agent`, `build_planner_agent`, `build_reporter_agent`, `invoke_react_agent`\n306: \n307: **验收**: `ls example/pcap-analyzer/tests/test_pcap_analyzer.py example/pcap-analyzer/tests/test_sandbox_runner.py example/pcap-analyzer/tests/test_agents.py` 三个文件均存在\n308: \n309: ---\n310: \n311: ## Dependency Graph\n312: \n313: ```\n314: T-001 (create directories) ──────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n315:                                                                           │\n316: T-002 (main.py) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n317: T-003 (manifest.yaml) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n318: T-004 (requirements.txt plugin) ──────────────────────────────────────────┤\n319:                                                                           ├── T-005 (provider/agentcube.yaml)\n320:                                                                           │\n321: T-005 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n322:                                                                           ├── T-006 (provider/agentcube.py)\n323:                                                                           │\n324: T-007 (tool schema yaml) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n325:                                                                           ├── T-008 (tool implementation.py)\n326:                                                                           │\n327: T-006 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n328: T-008 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n329:                                                                           ├── T-009 (docs: GUIDE, README, PRIVACY, .difyignore)\n330:                                                                           │\n331: T-010 (example dir + requirements.txt) ───────────────────────────────────┤\n332:                                                                           ├── T-011 (pcap_analyzer.py: config, agents, SandboxRunner)\n333:                                                                           │\n334: T-011 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n335:                                                                           ├── T-012 (pcap_analyzer.py: orchestration functions)\n336:                                                                           │\n337: T-012 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n338:                                                                           ├── T-013 (pcap_analyzer.py: FastAPI app + /analyze endpoint)\n339:                                                                           │\n340: T-011 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n341: T-013 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n342:                                                                           ├── T-014 (Dockerfile)\n343:                                                                           │\n344: T-013 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n345:                                                                           ├── T-015 (deployment.yaml)\n346:                                                                           │\n347: T-014 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n348: T-015 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n349:                                                                           ├── T-016 (example README)\n350:                                                                           │\n351: T-006 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n352: T-008 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n353:                                                                           ├── T-017 (Dify plugin tests)\n354:                                                                           │\n355: T-011 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n356: T-012 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n357: T-013 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n358:                                                                           └── T-018 (PCAP analyzer tests)\n359: ```\n360: \n361: ## Parallelizable Groups\n362: \n363: | Group | Tasks | Prerequisites |\n364: |-------|-------|---------------|\n365: | G1 | T-001 (create directories) | None |\n366: | G2 | T-002 (main.py), T-003 (manifest.yaml), T-004 (requirements.txt) | G1 |\n367: | G3 | T-005 (provider yaml), T-007 (tool schema yaml), T-010 (example dir + reqs) | G2 |\n368: | G4 | T-006 (provider.py), T-008 (tool.py) | G3 (T-005, T-007) |\n369: | G5 | T-009 (docs), T-011 (pcap_analyzer config/agents/runner) | G3 (T-010), G4 |\n370: | G6 | T-012 (orchestration), T-014 (Dockerfile) | G5 |\n371: | G7 | T-013 (FastAPI endpoint), T-015 (deployment.yaml), T-016 (example README) | G6 |\n372: | G8 | T-017 (Dify tests), T-018 (PCAP tests) | G4 (T-006, T-008), G7 (T-011, T-012, T-013) |\n373: \n374: ---\n375: \n376: ## Acceptance Criteria\n377: \n378: | # | Criterion | Command |\n379: |---|-----------|---------|\n380: | AC1 | Plugin directory structure exists with provider/ and tools/ subdirs | `ls -d integrations/dify-plugin/provider/ integrations/dify-plugin/tools/` 退出码 0 |\n381: | AC2 | `main.py` runs plugin with `MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120` | `grep 'MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120' integrations/dify-plugin/main.py` 有输出 |\n382: | AC3 | `manifest.yaml` has correct version, type, author, name, meta.runner | `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml')); assert d['version']=='0.0.2' and d['type']=='plugin' and d['meta']['runner']['language']=='python'\"` 退出码 0 |\n383: | AC4 | Plugin requirements pin dify-plugin and agentcube-sdk | `grep 'dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0' integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt` && `grep 'agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10' integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt` |\n384: | AC5 | Provider descriptor has identity, tools list, python source | `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml')); assert d['extra']['python']['source']=='provider/agentcube.py'\"` 退出码 0 |\n385: | AC6 | Provider class inherits ToolProvider with _validate_credentials | `grep 'class AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider(ToolProvider)' integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py` 有输出 |\n386: | AC7 | Tool schema has required router_url/workload_manager_url and optional language select | `python3 -c \"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml')); params={p['name']:p for p in d['parameters']}; assert params['router_url']['required'] and params['language']['type']=='select'\"` 退出码 0 |\n387: | AC8 | Tool class inherits Tool with _invoke and execute methods | `python3 -c \"import ast; tree=ast.parse(open('